Element stepped forward and followed Divebomb after Divebomb destroyed the 
missiles. He was annoyed, so he wasn't going to let Divebomb get away that 
easy.

"You shouldn't have attacked here, Decepticon." said Element in a growl and 
fired two missiles from each missile launcher. He mentally controlled all 
four so they would have a greater chance to hit Divebomb.
